---
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 md:py-32 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif">Dogfooding</h2>
      <p class="text-ash text-sm max-w-2xl mx-auto">We point pwnkit at pwnkit. Every push.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-night-lighter border border-border rounded-xl p-8 sm:p-10">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-crimson animate-pulse"></span>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif">pwnkit reviews its own source code</h3>
        </div>
        <span class="text-xs text-ash">On every push via GitHub Actions</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-smoke text-sm mb-6">pwnkit runs <code class="text-white/60">pwnkit review .</code> on its own repository. The same agentic pipeline that found 7 CVEs &mdash; pointed at itself. If it finds something, you'll see it here.</p>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
        <a href="https://pwnkit.com" class="inline-block">
          <img src="/badge/peaktwilight/pwnkit" alt="pwnkit verified" class="h-5" loading="lazy" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/peaktwilight/pwnkit/actions/workflows/self-scan.yml" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-ash hover:text-white/70 transition-colors font-mono">
          View CI runs
          <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-border pt-6 space-y-5">
        <p class="text-smoke text-sm font-medium">Set it up on your repo in 2 minutes:</p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-xs text-ash">1. Add to your GitHub Actions workflow:</p>
          <code class="block bg-night border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-xs text-smoke select-all font-mono overflow-x-auto">- run: npx pwnkit-cli review . --format json &gt; pwnkit-report.json</code>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-xs text-ash">2. Add the badge to your README:</p>
          <code class="block bg-night border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-xs text-smoke select-all font-mono overflow-x-auto">[![pwnkit](https://pwnkit.com/badge/ORG/REPO)](https://pwnkit.com)</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
